Package logicCircuits

Class LogicCircuit

java.lang.Object
logicCircuits.LogicCircuit
public class LogicCircuit extends Object
Author:
Dominik Baumann, Philipp Grzywaczyk A logic circuit / logic board is an assortment of connected gates.* The gates are organized in a twice-nested ArrayList. We use this instead of normal arrays, so we can dynamically increase the size. Adding / removing Gates as well as connecting them is done via their coordinates.
